&lt;p&gt;As promised here is the code. Its a small js driver basically
that runs on linux but porting it to windows or mac should be really straightforward. Do note if you decide to run it
how beautiful low level event driven JS in fact is. Such a treat after framework land.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/djuleAyo/lang-agnostic-steno&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;GitHub repo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t forget to install dependencies outside of npm (xdotool)&lt;/p&gt;
